L_SIZE, y // CELL_SIZE if start_phase: if count_pions(turn) == 0: place_pion(turn, grid_x, grid_y) turn = (turn + 1) % len(player_colors) if count_pions(turn) == 1: start_phase = False turn = 0 else: if check_neighbors(grid_x, grid_y, turn): result = pierre_feuille_ciseaux() if result == 0: place_pion(turn, grid_x, grid_y) elif result == 1: place_pion((turn + 1) % len(player_colors), grid_x, grid_y) else: # Le cas où pierre_feuille_ciseaux() retourne -1 (égalité) # Vous pouvez choisir de ne rien faire, ou d'appliquer une autre logique si nécessaire pass screen.fill(WHITE) draw_grid(screen) pygame.display.flip() clock.tick(60) if is_game_over(start_phase): winner = 0 if count_pions(0) > count_pions(1) else 1 print(\\"Le joueur\\", winner + 1, \\"a gagné!\\") break pygame.quit() sys.exit() if __name__ == \\"__main__\\": play_game() \`\`\` Maintenant, lorsque vous cliquez sur une case qui a un voisin de couleur différente, la fonction \`pierre_feuille_ciseaux()\` sera utilisée pour déterminer quel joueur remporte la case. Si c'est un match nul (résultat == -1), aucune action ne sera prise."},{"instruction":"Who are you ?","output":"I am an AI language model trained to answer questions and have conversations with users. I am not a human, but I am here to help and provide useful information."},{"instruction":"Fantasy RPG party: \\"The Lion\\" Duran Personality: Heroic, Determined, Honest Speech Pattern: Formal Before Fall from Grace: Knight in King Mungold's royal guard. Fall from Grace: Secret love affair with the king's daughter Elena. Equipment: Plate Armor, Bastard Sword, Kite Shield Speciality: Defensive Sword Fighting with Strong Counterattacks - \\"The Bear\\" Vancor Personality: Brave, Proud, Aggressive Speech Pattern: Slang Before Fall from Grace: Warrior fighting for gold and prestige. Fall from Grace: Betrayed and blamed by his former mates for a failed job. Equipment: Leather Armor, Greatsword, Throwing Axe Speciality: Aggressive Sword Fighting with Powerful 